Crules R. CHEEK, Trustee In Bankruptcy of Great Western Furniture Mfg. Co., a Corporation, Bankrupt, v. Alvin HOROWITZ. No. 9583. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Aug. 5, 1940. Samuel A. Miller, Walter G. Danielson, and Bertram H. Ross, all of Los Angeles, Cal, for appellant. Fred Horowitz and P. N. McCloskey, both of Los Angeles, Cal, for appellee.

Before DENMAN, MATHEWS, and HEALY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

On stipulation of counsel for respective parties, and good cause therefor appearing, ordered appeal dismissed, that a decree be filed and entered accordingly, and mandate issued forthwith.
